headline: West to Host Fourth-Quarter and Full-Year 2025 Conference Call
summary: West Pharmaceutical Services, Inc. (NYSE: WST), a global leader in innovative solutions for injectable drug administration, today announced that it will release fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 financial results before the market opens on Thursday, February 12, 2026, and will follow with a conference call to discuss the results and business expectations at 8:00 a.m. Eastern Time.
